description: Rubik is a sans serif font family with slightly rounded corners designed by Philipp Hubert and Sebastian Fischer at Hubert & Fischer as part of the Chrome Cube Lab project. Rubik One is the initial version of the Black roman style in the Rubik family, which has 5 weights. It is paired with Rubik Mono One, a monospaced variation of the design.
